<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_ab10f29a0d36.aspx"><b>无衣</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonab10f29a0d36">
<p>岂曰无衣？七兮。不如子之衣，安且吉兮。<br />岂曰无衣？六兮。不如子之衣，安且燠兮。</p>
